----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Data attribution
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
The dataset used by this project is the "Lending Club loan dataset for granting
models" (Zenodo record 11295916), licensed CC-BY-4.0. The dataset is downloaded
at runtime by `make data` and is NOT redistributed in this repository, except
for a small sample under tests/fixtures/ used for fast CI. Attribute the dataset
authors per CC-BY-4.0 when reusing it.
